node-1722339666383.name: RemoveDuplicates
node-1722339666383.sqlQuery:
SELECT
  *
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      *,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY product ORDER BY loadts DESC, counter DESC) as is_latest
    FROM
      cdf
  )
WHERE
  is_latest = 1;

node-1722339771608.name: MergeToTarget
node-1722339771608.sqlQuery:
MERGE INTO AwsDataCatalog.<your_curated_glue_catalog_db>.cds_material_attr t
USING (SELECT * FROM sdf) s on s.product = t.product
WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET * WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN INSERT *
